// The importance of English in the academic and professional spheres cannot be overstated. In higher education, a vast majority of prestigious scientific journals and research publications are in English. In the corporate world, multinational companies often adopt English as their official language for operations. Furthermore, the digital age is predominantly driven by English, with most programming languages, software interfaces, and online content being based in English. From navigating the internet to accessing global entertainment, a command of English opens up a world of information and opportunity.

